# Streamlit App Walkthrough (Audio Enabled)

## Summary
The virtual piano now produces real sound!

## New Features
- **Audio Feedback**: Plays [.wav](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/sounds/e1.wav) files (key notes) instantly when you press a key.
- **Polyphony**: Supports chords (multiple sounds playing at once).
- **Audio Engine**: Uses `pygame` for low-latency playback.

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run app.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
